- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility because modular forms have connections to number theory and algorithms for computing them efficiently. 
- cs.SC (Symbolic Computation) is a possibility because modular forms are often studied using symbolic manipulation and computer algebra systems.
